Design Variations Symbols are supported in up to nine weights and three scales. For optimal layout with text and other symbols, vertically align symbols with the adjacent text.
Margins Leading and trailing margins on the left and right side of each symbol can be adjusted by modifying the x-location of the margin guidelines. Modifications are automatically applied proportionally to all scales and weights.
